{
  "suggest": {
    "text" : "search_term",
    "mysuggest1"{
      "term" : {
        "field" : "field_name",
	"prefix_length":1,
	"suggest_mode":"missing/popular/always"
      }
    }
    "mysuggest2"{
      "term" : {
        "field" : "field_name"
      }
    }
  }
}

suggest_mode - missing : Only provide suggestions for suggest text terms that are not in the index. This is the default.
suggest_mode - popular : Only suggest suggestions that occur in more docs than the original suggest text term
suggest_mode - always : Suggest any matching suggestions based on terms in the suggest text
size : The maximum corrections to be returned
prefix_length : The number of minimal prefix characters that must match in order be a candidate for suggestions
min_word_length : The minimum length a suggest text term must have in order to be included. Defaults to 4.


